flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> A[User uploads document]
  A --> B[Validate file type and size]
  B --> C{Valid?}
  C -- No --> X[Reject upload with error]
  X --> End([End])

  C -- Yes --> D[Store original file]
  D --> E[Extract text]
  E --> F[Chunk content]
  F --> G[Generate embeddings]
  G --> H[Upsert vectors to Qdrant]
  H --> I[Persist chunk metadata]
  I --> J[Mark document as indexed]
  J --> K[Notify user status complete]
  K --> End
